sequenceDiagram
    participant User as React Frontend (Millions of Users)
    participant Worker as Cloudflare Worker
    participant KV as Cloudflare KV (categories.json)
    participant Microservice as Product Category Microservice (Spring Boot + Postgres)

    User->>Worker: GET /categories.json
    Worker->>KV: Fetch categories
    KV-->>Worker: JSON data
    Worker-->>User: Return categories.json

    Microservice->>Worker: POST /categories.json (with API Token)
    Worker->>KV: Update categories
    Worker-->>Microservice: Success { "success": true }
